version_description: Optimization, Japanese and German language support.
The Skullcandy app now supports Crusher ANC, Indy Evo, Indy Fuel and Push Ultra. New product setup information and user guides are constantly being added.

The Skullcandy App now supports Indy Evo, Indy Fuel,  Push Ultra, and select Crusher headphones. We improved linking compatibility of Skullcandy products to the Skullcandy App as well as other bug fixes.
The Skullcandy App supports Crusher Evo, Crusher ANC, Indy Evo, Indy Fuel, and Push Ultra. We further improved linking compatibility of Skullcandy products to the Skullcandy App.

Meet the completely redesigned Skullcandy App. Tune your Skullcandy audio device, explore the Skullcandy brand and get customer service help.

CURRENT COMPATIBLE PRODUCTS INCLUDE:
- Crusher ANC
- Crusher Evo
- Indy Evo
- Indy Fuel
- Push Ultra
